    "description": "Fires slow, steeply arcing rounds that split into three shortly after being fired. Weapon bonuses: 35% chance to fire an extra shot and +30% critical hit damage (pre-add). Note that most assault rifles (excluding Jakobs) carry -20% critical hit damage (scale)."
